measurements.description: Thirty-eight flowers and 13 buds on five arched up to 77.5-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals broadly acuminate, bronze-orange, darker veins; lip cream, keels yellow speckled maroon, side lobes flushed bronze-orange, midlobe blotched dark maroon; column cream flushed bronze ventrally, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
